reviewText: Anything Jolewis does is so far above competition that makes you want to return other peoples merchandise, a true genius in the field.

Anybody reading this probably already knows the Joe Lewis history in martial arts. If you don't, then you should probably check it out. This video is a great routine to add power to your striking and if you are not already doing something similar you will notice results in a short time. I am very happy I made the purchase.
